♪La la♪

354
00:17:43,850 --> 00:17:45,840
♪No line divides the border♪

355
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:48,620
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

356
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:50,990
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

357
00:17:50,990 --> 00:17:53,680
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

358
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:56,890
♪Hey hey hey♪

359
00:17:58,220 --> 00:18:00,040
♪Hey hey hey♪

360
